title: 组合总和 II | labuladong 算法可视化

You need to enable JavaScript to run this app. 页面加载失败，请尝试清除浏览器缓存并刷新页面。 Error occurred when loading the page, please try to clear browser cache and refresh the page. window.__viz = {
        data: ''
    } var combinationSum2 = function(candidates, target) {
    let res = [];
    let trackSum = 0;
    // 排序，以便于处理相同元素
    let sortedCandidates = candidates.sort((a, b) => a - b);

    // 回溯函数
    // @visualize status(nums.slice(0, start))
    let backtrack = function(nums, start, track) {
        // 达到目标和，找到符合条件的组合，记录结果
        if (trackSum === target) {
            // @visualize color *backtrack._vizNode #green
            res.push([...track]);
            return;
        }
        // 先剪枝，超过目标和，直接结束
        if (trackSum > target) {
            return;
        }
        // 回溯算法标准框架
        for (let i = start; i < nums.length; i++) {
            // 剪枝逻辑，值相同的树枝，只遍历第一条
            if (i > start && nums[i] === nums[i - 1]) {
                continue;
            }
            // 做选择
            // @visualize choose(nums[i])
            track.push(nums[i]);
            trackSum += nums[i];
            // 递归遍历下一层回溯树
            backtrack(nums, i + 1, track);
            // 撤销选择
            // @visualize unchoose()
            track.pop();
            trackSum -= nums[i];
        }
    }

    backtrack(sortedCandidates, 0, []);
    return res;
};

let result = combinationSum2([1,2,3,2,3], 7)
 window.onerror = function (message, source, lineno, colno, error) {
        const root = document.getElementById('root');
        if (!root || !root.innerHTML.trim()) {
            console.log('window on error:', error, message)
            document.getElementById('error-message').style.display = 'block';
        }
    };

    // MutationObserver to monitor changes in #root
    const observer = new MutationObserver(function (mutations) {
        const root = document.getElementById('root');
        if (root && root.innerHTML.trim()) {
            document.getElementById('error-message').style.display = 'none';
            window.onerror = null; // Remove the window.onerror listener
            observer.disconnect(); // Stop observing
        }
    });

    // Observe changes in the child list of #root
    observer.observe(document.getElementById('root'), {
        childList: true,
        subtree: true
    });
